Follyer. This young woman [
Mary Connelly
] and I were drinking in a box, and the prisoner and a sailor came in, and the prisoner and the sailor were arguing.

Middleton. Yes; we met them on the highway, Robins had given us a description of them before, that, the old man was dressed in a dark coat, and the young man, in a lose light coloured coat;
John Robins
, charged them with robbing him, and they said they knew nothing of him, but they did confess before the morning, that they were the men.

Hyam Aaron . On the 20th of September, a woman who lives a little way off me, sent for me, I found the Court all in an uproar; and I heard that Mrs. Lazarus was robbed;
Reuben Isaac
told us, he was walking in Moor Fields, and saw the prisoner with a Jew man that goes by the name of White, but his name is Cokey Levi.
